# Patterns the api-watchdog looks for on each role's tmux pane to flag
# transient, retryable GitHub Copilot / Anthropic API / network errors.
# One extended regex per line; case-insensitive.
#
# TODO(copilot-port): observe real Copilot CLI error messages and add patterns
# TODO(copilot-port): check if Copilot shows rate-limit errors differently than Claude

# Copilot-specific
rate.limit
quota.*exceeded
premium.*request
Request.*failed
Copilot.*unavailable
Copilot.*error

# Anthropic API (if Copilot routes through Anthropic)
API Error.*Rate limit
API Error.*temporarily limiting requests
API Error.*Overloaded

# Network / generic
Connection error
Network error
ECONNRESET
ETIMEDOUT
fetch failed
socket hang up
